## 20) Full rebuild command sequence (copy-paste)

```bash
mkdir Product_Label_Scanner
cd Product_Label_Scanner
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install Django djangorestframework easyocr opencv-python-headless dateparser spacy
pip freeze > requirements.txt

django-admin startproject label_scanner .
python manage.py startapp scanner

python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
```

Then create all files explained above.

---

## 21) What to do next (learning path)

1. Build regex-only version first and make it stable.
2. Add OpenCV preprocessing and compare OCR quality.
3. Add spaCy NER and fallback logic.
4. Add test cases for each bug you discover.
5. Improve extraction rules using real label data.

---

If you follow this file section-by-section, you can recreate the whole project yourself from zero and understand every layer.
